      </para></chapter><chapter xml:id="ID_S1KDTOOLS-A-00-00-00-00A-040B-D"><info><title>s1kd-tools</title><subtitle>Description</subtitle><date>2020-05-01</date><bibliomisc role="publication.title">s1kd-tools</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="publication.author">khzae.net</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="page.header.logo">
