      </bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="producedby.blurb">Produced by: khzae.net</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="data.module.code">S1KDTOOLS-A-00-00-00-00A-040B-D</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="publication.code">S1KDTOOLS-KHZAE-00000-00</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="classification">UNCLASSIFIED</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="applicability">Version: 3.3.0</bibliomisc></info><bridgehead renderas="centerhead">References</bridgehead><table pgwide="1" frame="topbot" colsep="0" role="refs"><title>References</title><tgroup cols="2" align="left"><thead><row><entry>Data module/Technical publication</entry><entry>Title</entry></row></thead><tbody rowsep="0"><row><entry><link xlink:href="https://github.com/kibook/S1000D-XSL-Stylesheets">https://github.com/kibook/S1000D-XSL-Stylesheets</link></entry><entry>S1000D XSL stylesheets</entry></row><row><entry><link xlink:href="https://github.com/kibook/s1kd-tools">https://github.com/kibook/s1kd-tools</link></entry><entry>s1kd-tools</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><bridgehead renderas="centerhead">Description</bridgehead>
      <section>
        <title>General</title>
        <para><emphasis role="bold">s1kd-tools</emphasis> are a set of small tools for manipulating S1000D data. They are maintained at <link xlink:href="https://github.com/kibook/s1kd-tools">https://github.com/kibook/s1kd-tools</link>.</para>
        <para>This publication is meant to serve as an example of an S1000D data set produced using these tools. The stylesheets used to produce this PDF can be found at <link xlink:href="https://github.com/kibook/S1000D-XSL-Stylesheets">https://github.com/kibook/S1000D-XSL-Stylesheets</link></para>
      </section>
    </chapter><chapter xml:id="ID_S1KDTOOLS-A-00-00-00-00A-018A-D"><info><title>s1kd-tools</title><subtitle>Introduction</subtitle><date>2020-05-01</date><bibliomisc role="publication.title">s1kd-tools</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="publication.author">khzae.net</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="page.header.logo">
        <inlinemediaobject><imageobject xmlns:ier="InfoEntityResolver"><imagedata align="center" fileref="custom/ICN-S1KDTOOLS-A-000000-A-KHZAE-00001-A-001-01.PNG" depth="12mm" contentdepth="12mm"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>
      </bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="producedby.blurb">Produced by: khzae.net</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="data.module.code">S1KDTOOLS-A-00-00-00-00A-018A-D</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="publication.code">S1KDTOOLS-KHZAE-00000-00</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="classification">UNCLASSIFIED</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="applicability">Version: 3.3.0</bibliomisc></info><bridgehead renderas="centerhead">References</bridgehead><table pgwide="1" frame="topbot" colsep="0" role="refs"><title>References</title><tgroup cols="2" align="left"><thead><row><entry>Data module/Technical publication</entry><entry>Title</entry></row></thead><tbody rowsep="0"><row><entry><link xlink:href="https://www.nccu.edu.tw/">https://www.nccu.edu.tw/</link></entry><entry>nccu官網</entry></row><row><entry><link xlink:href="https://www.soic.org.tw/">https://www.soic.org.tw/</link></entry><entry>船舶中心網站</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><bridgehead renderas="centerhead">Description</bridgehead>
      <section>
        <title>政大創新國際學系（International College of Innovation, NCCU） 三軌課程設計</title>
        <para>
    全球治理（Global Governance）
  </para>
        <para>
    永續與社會（Sustainability &amp; Society）
  </para>
        <para>
    資料分析（Data Analytics）
  </para>
        <para>
    三軌課程各自具備明確的學習方向，但共同目標是讓學生在面對高度變動的全球環境時，具備理解、分析與行動的能力。詳見<link xlink:href="https://www.nccu.edu.tw/">https://www.nccu.edu.tw/</link>
  </para>
        <section id="ID_S1KDTOOLS-A-00-00-00-00A-018A-D-par-0001">
          <title>全球治理</title>
          <para>
      此課程軌聚焦於全球政治互動、國際制度與民主相關議題，培養學生對世界局勢的判讀能力與公共參與視野。
    </para>
        </section>
        <section id="ID_S1KDTOOLS-A-00-00-00-00A-018A-D-par-0002">
          <title>永續與社會</title>
          <para>
      此課程軌強調自然、生態、科技與社會之間的關係，引導學生理解當代世界的多重脆弱性，並思考永續發展的可能。
    </para>
        </section>
        <section id="ID_S1KDTOOLS-A-00-00-00-00A-018A-D-par-0003">
          <title>資料分析</title>
          <para>
      此課程軌介紹資料處理、分析與科技應用，使學生能運用量化工具理解社會問題，並在跨領域情境中提出具體解方。
    </para>
        </section>
      </section>
