    </chapter><chapter xml:id="ID_S1KDTOOLS-A-41-31-00-00A-040A-D"><info><title>中央時鐘系統</title><subtitle>Description</subtitle><date>2025-11-23</date><bibliomisc role="publication.title">s1kd-tools</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="publication.author">khzae.net</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="page.header.logo">
        <inlinemediaobject><imageobject xmlns:ier="InfoEntityResolver"><imagedata align="center" fileref="custom/ICN-S1KDTOOLS-A-000000-A-KHZAE-00001-A-001-01.PNG" depth="12mm" contentdepth="12mm"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>
      </bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="producedby.blurb">Produced by: khzae.net</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="data.module.code">S1KDTOOLS-A-41-31-00-00A-040A-D</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="publication.code">S1KDTOOLS-KHZAE-00000-00</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="classification">UNCLASSIFIED</bibliomisc><bibliomisc role="applicability">Version: 3.3.0</bibliomisc></info><bridgehead renderas="centerhead">References</bridgehead><table pgwide="1" frame="topbot" colsep="0" role="refs"><title>References</title><tgroup cols="2" align="left"><thead><row><entry>Data module/Technical publication</entry><entry>Title</entry></row></thead><tbody rowsep="0"><row><entry>None</entry><entry/></row></tbody></tgroup></table><bridgehead renderas="centerhead">Description</bridgehead>
      <para>This is a placeholder for the description content.</para>
      <section>
        <title>功能</title>
        <para>
    中央時鐘系統透過主鐘將時間訊號傳送至全艦各子鐘與整合式儎臺管理系統。
  </para>
        <section id="ID_S1KDTOOLS-A-41-31-00-00A-040A-D-par-0001">
          <title>系統識別區分</title>
          <para>
      重要性: 次要系統(SV)，備便狀態:第1級系統(1)。
    </para>
        </section>
        <section id="ID_S1KDTOOLS-A-41-31-00-00A-040A-D-par-0002">
          <title>概述</title>
          <para>
      中央時鐘系統電力來源為DC 24V來自於B-2D分電箱，利用整合式艦橋管理系統透過IF-2550將GPS訊號傳送至中央時鐘的主鐘，主鐘再傳送訊號到各子鐘與整合式儎臺管理系統；其中，整合式艦橋系統透過自身的裝備櫃傳送一組NTP訊號至戰情室一子鐘，系統架構圖如<link linkend="ID_S1KDTOOLS-A-41-31-00-00A-040A-D-fig_001">Fig 1</link>。
    </para>
        </section>
      </section>
    
      <figure id="ID_S1KDTOOLS-A-41-31-00-00A-040A-D-fig_001" label="1" pgwide="1"><title>中央時鐘系統架構圖</title><mediaobject><imageobject xmlns:ier="InfoEntityResolver"><imagedata align="center" fileref="custom/ICN-S1KDTOOLS-A-000000-A-KHZAE-00301-A-001-01.PNG" width="100%" scalefit="1"/></imageobject><caption role="icn"><para>ICN-S1KDTOOLS-A-000000-A-KHZAE-00301-A-001-01</para></caption><caption role="title"><para>Fig 1  中央時鐘系統架構圖</para></caption></mediaobject></figure>
